name: AAA Boss
description:
Pixel Boss Elite. You've been selectively invited to join this tier. 

* VIP fingerprint access to our physical club. AAA members are able to access our facilities 24/7 and use it as your own exclusive space.

* Some additional perks include the ability to host multiple events at our club (limited to AAA members only) and exclusive access to the Pixel Boss Committee. 

* Visit our Website: [Pixel Boss Club](https://pixelboss.io/club/)
* Follow us on Twitter: [@PixelBoss_](https://twitter.com/PixelBoss_)
